{
  "comment_text": {
    "dhp41:4": "As the sacrificed beast “lies there useless as a block of wood” (<i lang='pi' translate='no'>dārveva tarhi bhūto ’narthyaḥ śete</i>, Śatapatha Brāhmaṇa 3.8.3.15). "
  },
