  "root_text": {
    "dhp33:0.1": "Khuddakanikāya ",
    "dhp33:0.2": "Dhammapada ",
    "dhp33:0.3": "Cittavagga ",
    "dhp33:0.4": "Meghiyattheravatthu ",
    "dhp33:1": "Phandanaṁ capalaṁ cittaṁ, ",
    "dhp33:2": "dūrakkhaṁ dunnivārayaṁ; ",
    "dhp33:3": "Ujuṁ karoti medhāvī, ",
    "dhp33:4": "usukārova tejanaṁ. ",
    "dhp34:1": "Vārijova thale khitto, ",
    "dhp34:2": "okamokataubbhato; ",
    "dhp34:3": "Pariphandatidaṁ cittaṁ, ",
    "dhp34:4": "māradheyyaṁ pahātave. ",
    "dhp35:0": "Aññatarabhikkhuvatthu ",
    "dhp35:1": "Dunniggahassa lahuno, ",
    "dhp35:2": "yatthakāmanipātino; ",
    "dhp35:3": "Cittassa damatho sādhu, ",
    "dhp35:4": "cittaṁ dantaṁ sukhāvahaṁ. ",
    "dhp36:0": "Aññataraukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuvatthu ",
    "dhp36:1": "Sududdasaṁ sunipuṇaṁ, ",
    "dhp36:2": "yatthakāmanipātinaṁ; ",
    "dhp36:3": "Cittaṁ rakkhetha medhāvī, ",
    "dhp36:4": "cittaṁ guttaṁ sukhāvahaṁ. ",
    "dhp37:0": "Saṅgharakkhitabhāgineyyattheravatthu ",
    "dhp37:1": "Dūraṅgamaṁ ekacaraṁ, ",
    "dhp37:2": "asarīraṁ guhāsayaṁ; ",
    "dhp37:3": "Ye cittaṁ saṁyamissanti, ",
    "dhp37:4": "mokkhanti mārabandhanā. ",
    "dhp38:0": "Cittahatthattheravatthu ",
    "dhp38:1": "Anavaṭṭhitacittassa, ",
    "dhp38:2": "saddhammaṁ avijānato; ",
    "dhp38:3": "Pariplavapasādassa, ",
    "dhp38:4": "paññā na paripūrati. ",
    "dhp39:1": "Anavassutacittassa, ",
    "dhp39:2": "ananvāhatacetaso; ",
    "dhp39:3": "Puññapāpapahīnassa, ",
    "dhp39:4": "natthi jāgarato bhayaṁ. ",
    "dhp40:0": "Pañcasatabhikkhuvatthu ",
    "dhp40:1": "Kumbhūpamaṁ kāyamimaṁ viditvā, ",
    "dhp40:2": "Nagarūpamaṁ cittamidaṁ ṭhapetvā; ",
    "dhp40:3": "Yodhetha māraṁ paññāvudhena, ",
    "dhp40:4": "Jitañca rakkhe anivesano siyā. ",
    "dhp41:0": "Pūtigattatissattheravatthu ",
    "dhp41:1": "Aciraṁ vatayaṁ kāyo, ",
    "dhp41:2": "pathaviṁ adhisessati; ",
    "dhp41:3": "Chuddho apetaviññāṇo, ",
    "dhp41:4": "niratthaṁva kaliṅgaraṁ. ",
    "dhp42:0": "Nandagopālakavatthu ",
    "dhp42:1": "Diso disaṁ yaṁ taṁ kayirā, ",
    "dhp42:2": "verī vā pana verinaṁ; ",
    "dhp42:3": "Micchāpaṇihitaṁ cittaṁ, ",
    "dhp42:4": "pāpiyo naṁ tato kare. ",
    "dhp43:0": "Soreyyavatthu ",
    "dhp43:1": "Na taṁ mātā pitā kayirā, ",
    "dhp43:2": "aññe vāpi ca ñātakā; ",
    "dhp43:3": "Sammāpaṇihitaṁ cittaṁ, ",
    "dhp43:4": "seyyaso naṁ tato kare. ",
    "dhp43:5": "Cittavaggo tatiyo. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "dhp33:0.1": "Minor Collection ",
    "dhp33:0.2": "Sayings of the Dhamma 33–43 ",
    "dhp33:0.3": "3. The Mind ",
    "dhp33:1": "The mind quivers and shakes, ",
    "dhp33:2": "hard to guard, hard to curb. ",
    "dhp33:3": "The discerning straighten it out, ",
    "dhp33:4": "like a fletcher straightens an arrow. ",
    "dhp34:1": "Like a fish pulled from the sea ",
    "dhp34:2": "and cast upon the shore, ",
    "dhp34:3": "this mind flounders about, ",
    "dhp34:4": "trying to throw off Māra’s dominion. ",
    "dhp35:1": "Hard to hold back, flighty, ",
    "dhp35:2": "alighting where it will; ",
    "dhp35:3": "it’s good to tame the mind; ",
    "dhp35:4": "a tamed mind leads to bliss. ",
    "dhp36:1": "So hard to see, so subtle, ",
    "dhp36:2": "alighting where it will; ",
    "dhp36:3": "the discerning protect the mind, ",
    "dhp36:4": "a guarded mind leads to bliss. ",
    "dhp37:1": "The mind travels far, wandering alone; ",
    "dhp37:2": "incorporeal, it lies hidden in the heart. ",
    "dhp37:3": "Those who will restrain the mind ",
    "dhp37:4": "are freed from Māra’s bonds. ",
    "dhp38:1": "Those of unsteady mind, ",
    "dhp38:2": "who don’t understand the true teaching, ",
    "dhp38:3": "and whose confidence wavers, ",
    "dhp38:4": "do not perfect their wisdom. ",
    "dhp39:1": "One whose mind is not festering, ",
    "dhp39:2": "whose heart is undamaged, ",
    "dhp39:3": "who’s given up right and wrong, ",
    "dhp39:4": "alert, has nothing to fear. ",
    "dhp40:1": "Knowing this body breaks like a pot, ",
    "dhp40:2": "and fortifying the mind like a citadel, ",
    "dhp40:3": "attack Māra with the sword of wisdom, ",
    "dhp40:4": "guard your conquest, and never settle. ",
    "dhp41:1": "All too soon this body ",
    "dhp41:2": "will lie upon the earth, ",
    "dhp41:3": "bereft of consciousness, ",
    "dhp41:4": "tossed aside like a worthless log. ",
    "dhp42:1": "A wrongly directed mind ",
    "dhp42:2": "would do you more harm ",
    "dhp42:3": "than a hater to the hated, ",
    "dhp42:4": "or an enemy to their foe. ",
    "dhp43:1": "A rightly directed mind ",
    "dhp43:2": "would do you more good ",
    "dhp43:3": "than your mother or father ",
    "dhp43:4": "or any other relative. "
  },
